{{Campaignbox 伊拉克內戰}}
'''安巴爾衝突'''是於2013年12月30日起，在[[伊拉克|伊拉克]][[安巴爾省|安巴爾省]]爆發的軍事衝突。事件的起因為伊拉克的安全部隊掃蕩位在[[拉馬迪|拉馬迪]]的一個[[遜尼派|遜尼派]]抗議營，部族民兵憤而開戰。12月31日，政府軍為了緩和情勢而選擇撤出安巴爾省，此後來自[[伊拉克和黎凡特伊斯蘭國|伊拉克和黎凡特伊斯蘭國]]（ISIL）的民兵進一步攻佔以遜尼派為多數的城市[[費盧傑|費盧傑]]和拉馬迪部分區域。許多拉馬迪的地方民兵則決定相互聯合，與政府軍共同對抗ISIL。

== 背景 ==
{{Expand section|date=2014年1月}}
2013年12月30日，當天安全部隊開始拆毀一個遜尼派反政府的主要地點，工作持續了兩天才結束。2014年1月1日，拉馬迪的民兵與安全部隊發生零星衝突，四座警察局遭到縱火，直至隔天才平息。隨後，戰火蔓延至費盧傑，當地警察被迫放棄了許多據點，民兵和武裝份子則焚燒警察局。

=== 參與組織 ===
反對派除了來自ISIL之外，還包括許多非ISIS武裝組織，例如遜尼派組織[[納克什班迪指揮軍|納克什班迪指揮軍]]（JRTN）也被指稱參與其中<ref name="jrtn"/>。其他像是規模最大的非ISIL組織部族革命軍事委員會，內部也包含了一些JRTN、{{link-en|1920革命旅|1920 Revolution Brigade}}、{{link-en|伊拉克伊斯蘭軍|Islamic Army in Iraq}}、{{link-en|聖戰和解放最高司令部|Jaish al-Rashideen}}、{{link-en|伊拉克哈瑪斯|Hamas of Iraq}}及前屬{{link-en|聖戰諮詢委員會|Mujahideen Shura Council (Iraq)}}的{{link-en|阿布都拉·賈納比|Abdullah al-Janabi}}<ref name="FP">{{cite news |last=Sowell |first=Kirk H. |date=2014-01-15 |title=Maliki's Anbar Blunder |url=http://mideastafrica.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2014/01/15/maliki_s_anbar_blunder |newspaper= |location= |publisher=Foreign Policy |accessdate= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140705054624/http://mideastafrica.foreignpolicy.com/posts/2014/01/15/maliki_s_anbar_blunder |archivedate=2014-07-05 }}</ref>等成員。

第二個組織則是由敘克·阿里·哈坦·蘇里曼（Sheikh Ali Hatem Suleiman）領導的安巴爾民兵革命委員會。此團體和革命軍事委員會不同，並不積極主張推翻伊拉克政府，而認為於政府軍的侵略下保衛[[安巴爾省|安巴爾省]]是首要任務<ref name="FP"/>。

第三個組織被稱作驕傲和尊嚴軍。這個團體也是由上述的蘇里曼先前在{{link-en|2013年哈威賈衝突|2013 Hawija clashes}}時創建的同名組織分裂而來，沒有明確的領導與幹部，結構相當鬆散<ref name="FP"/>。

== 衝突過程 ==
2013年12月30日，伊拉克總理[[努里·馬利基|努里·馬利基]]表示政府軍將會離開安巴爾省幾個狀況動盪不安的城市，但隔天即被推翻。1月2日，政府軍仍於拉馬迪城外活動<ref name="The Daily Star">{{cite news|title=Qaeda-linked fighters control parts of two Iraq cities|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-02/242879-qaeda-linked-militants-control-half-of-iraqs-fallujah-security.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-02|accessdate=2014-01-17|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019211055/http://www.dailystar.com.lb//News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-02/242879-qaeda-linked-militants-control-half-of-iraqs-fallujah-security.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2014年1月3日，[[蓋達|蓋達組織]]的相關民兵於衝突中取得進展，並攻下費盧傑的數座警察局。根據警察隊長表示，當天早晨民兵和ISIL攻佔拉馬迪市中心部分區域，並在一條街道上佈下狙擊手。一名警官表示政府軍已再度進入費盧傑，但仍有約四分之一的區域由ISIL和民兵控制，軍隊與親政府民兵暫時休戰，並聯手包圍該城{{Citation needed|date=January 2014}}。然而，另一名警官則表示雖然軍隊已部署在城市附近，但尚未進入費盧傑城中<ref>{{cite news|title=Militants make gains in Iraq city: police|url=http://english.al-akhbar.com/node/18098|newspaper=Al Akhbar|date=2014-01-03|accessdate=2014-01-17|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019092252/http://english.al-akhbar.com/node/18098|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Al-Qaeda militants make gains in Iraq city: police|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-03/242996-al-qaeda-militants-make-gains-in-iraq-city-police.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-03|accessdate=2014-01-03|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019211133/http://www.dailystar.com.lb//News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-03/242996-al-qaeda-militants-make-gains-in-iraq-city-police.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該日稍早時，超過百人於政府軍和武裝份子的交戰中喪生<ref>{{cite news|title=More than 100 die as Iraq battles Al-Qaeda|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-04/243086-more-than-100-die-as-iraq-battles-al-qaeda.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-04|accessdate=2014-01-17|archive-date=2018-07-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725033653/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-04/243086-more-than-100-die-as-iraq-battles-al-qaeda.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月4日，政府軍失去對費盧傑的控制權<ref>{{cite news|title=Fallujah outside Iraq government control: security official|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-04/243100-fallujah-outside-iraq-government-control-security-official.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-04|accessdate=2014-01-17|archive-date=2014-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104212909/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-04/243100-fallujah-outside-iraq-government-control-security-official.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據民兵領導者和官員的說法，政府軍為了收復該城，一度動用[[迫擊砲|迫擊砲]]轟炸，造成至少八人死亡。一份未具名的醫療資料則指出另外30人於轟炸中受傷<ref>{{cite news|title=Iraq army shells Falluja to dislodge Qaeda, tribes|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-04/243100-fallujah-outside-iraq-government-control-security-official.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-04|accessdate=2014-01-04|archive-date=2014-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140104212909/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-04/243100-fallujah-outside-iraq-government-control-security-official.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月6日，政府軍在當地民兵的協助下收復拉馬迪市中心，但是周圍區域的衝突至隔日仍持續發生。市中心、政府機關、醫院和市場則相繼開放<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/01/07/us-iraq-anbar-idUSBREA060HL20140107|title=Iraq moves up tanks, guns for looming Falluja assault|agency=[[路透社|路透社]]|date=2014-01-07|accessdate=2014-01-17|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924192231/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/01/07/us-iraq-anbar-idUSBREA060HL20140107|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

1月7日，政府軍發射火箭攻擊拉馬迪的武裝份子，成功造成25人陣亡<ref>{{cite news|title=Iraq missile strikes kill 25 militants: ministry|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-07/243326-iraq-missile-strikes-kill-25-militants-ministry.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-07|accessdate=2014-01-07|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019212047/http://www.dailystar.com.lb//News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-07/243326-iraq-missile-strikes-kill-25-militants-ministry.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同日，身份不明的槍手襲擊[[薩邁拉|薩邁拉]]北方的一個高速公路安全檢查站，擊殺了七名警察，且其中一位是隊長。雖然沒有組織承認犯案，但警方推測為ISIL武裝份子所為<ref>{{cite news|title=Gunmen kill 7 Iraqi policemen in checkpoint attack|url=http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2014/01/07/344323/gunmen-kill-7-iraqi-policemen/|date=2014-01-07|publisher=Press TV|accessdate=2014-01-17|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924134608/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2014/01/07/344323/gunmen-kill-7-iraqi-policemen/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月8日，ISIL控制了安巴爾省境內的城市庫瑪（Al-Karmah）<ref name="nytimes.com"/>、錫特（Hīt）、卡第耶（Khaldiyah）<ref name="Iraq Update #41: Showdown in Anbar"/>、[[哈迪塞|哈迪塞]]、艾昆（Al Qaim）<ref name="lwj">{{cite news|title=Al Qaeda, tribal allies 'control' Fallujah|url=http://www.longwarjournal.org/archives/2014/01/al_qaeda_tribal_alli.php|accessdate=2014-01-04|newspaper=Long War Journal|archive-date=2020-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201218212018/https://www.longwarjournal.org/archives/2014/01/al_qaeda_tribal_alli.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>和拉馬迪<ref name="dailystar.com.lb"/>、阿布賈拉比（Abu Ghraib）的部分地區<ref name="iswiraq.blogspot.com"/>，此外還有數個較小規模的住區<ref name="reuters.com"/>。同日，一位未具名的警察隊長證實政府軍和親政府民兵發動徹夜攻擊，試圖將ISIL趕出拉馬迪南區，但經過七個小時的戰鬥後被武裝份子擊退<ref>{{cite news|title=ISIL calls on Iraq Sunnis to keep fighting|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/01/isil-calls-iraq-sunnis-keep-fighting-2014186554213170.html|publisher=[[半島電視台|半島電視台]]|accessdate=2014-01-17|archive-date=2020-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918150247/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/01/isil-calls-iraq-sunnis-keep-fighting-2014186554213170.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月9日，政府軍憑藉[[戰車|戰車]]的支援下，於拉馬迪和費盧傑之間的布巴里（Al-bubali）與ISIL爆發戰鬥<ref>{{cite news|title=Heavy clashes as Iraq fighting sparks rights worries|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-09/243565-heavy-clashes-as-iraq-fighting-sparks-rights-worries.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-09|accessdate=2014-01-09|archive-date=2019-11-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191128223846/http://www.dailystar.com.lb//News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-09/243565-heavy-clashes-as-iraq-fighting-sparks-rights-worries.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月9日，ISIL再度和政府軍於布巴里發生衝突<ref>{{cite news|title=Fighters clash with Iraqi forces in Anbar|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/01/fighters-clash-with-iraqi-forces-anbar-2014110143456424894.html|publisher=[[半島電視台|半島電視台]]|date=2014-01-10|accessdate=2014-01-17|archive-date=2019-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191111164202/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2014/01/fighters-clash-with-iraqi-forces-anbar-2014110143456424894.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同日，政府軍和民兵收復拉馬迪的兩個區域<ref>{{cite news|title=Tribes, police seize parts of Iraq city from militants|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-10/243724-tribes-police-retake-parts-of-iraqs-ramadi-commander.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-10|accessdate=2014-01-17|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211013144/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-10/243724-tribes-police-retake-parts-of-iraqs-ramadi-commander.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月14日，包括ISIL在內的反政府遜尼派民兵攻佔了拉馬迪許多地區<ref>{{cite news|title=Sunni gunmen seize more turf in Iraq's Ramadi: police|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-14/244019-sunni-gunmen-seize-more-turf-in-iraqs-ramadi-police.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-14|accessdate=2014-01-17|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130090935/http://www.dailystar.com.lb//News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-14/244019-sunni-gunmen-seize-more-turf-in-iraqs-ramadi-police.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月16日，政府軍在遜尼派民兵協助下反擊ISIL，收復了薩格拉維亞赫（Saqlawiyah）<ref name="Press TV"/>。

1月17日，費盧傑城內的ISIL武裝份子呼籲民眾加入對抗政府的戰鬥，但在該日稍早時，伊拉克媒體報導政府軍已收復拉馬迪的一些關鍵區域<ref>{{cite news|title=Militants call on Fallujah people to join fight|url=http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2014/01/17/346052/militants-call-on-people-to-join-fight/|publisher=Press TV|date=2014-01-17|accessdate=2014-01-17|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924134621/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2014/01/17/346052/militants-call-on-people-to-join-fight/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月19日，政府軍對拉馬迪發動攻擊<ref>{{cite news|title=Iraqi army launches operation in Ramadi: officials|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-19/244519-iraqi-army-launches-operation-in-ramadi-officials.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-19|accessdate=2014-02-01|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202184409/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-19/244519-iraqi-army-launches-operation-in-ramadi-officials.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但並不順利，共有八名警察及民兵陣亡<ref>{{cite news|title=8 Iraqi police and tribesmen killed fighting Al Qaeda|url=http://in.reuters.com/article/2014/01/19/iraq-violence-idINDEEA0I08U20140119|date=2014-01-19|publisher=[[路透社|路透社]]|accessdate=2014-02-01|archive-date=2015-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150128055549/http://in.reuters.com/article/2014/01/19/iraq-violence-idINDEEA0I08U20140119|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。隔日，一位未具名的伊拉克官員宣稱ISIL具有足夠的重型武器{{where|date=2014年1月}}<!--https://en.wikipedia.org/w/index.php?title=Anbar_clashes_(2013%E2%80%9314)&diff=591636937&oldid=591593807-->威脅首都[[巴格達|巴格達]]<ref>{{cite news|title=Official: Al-Qaeda has enough arms to take Baghdad|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-20/244642-official-al-qaeda-has-enough-arms-to-take-baghdad.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|newspaper=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-20|accessdate=2014-02-01|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019214002/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-20/244642-official-al-qaeda-has-enough-arms-to-take-baghdad.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月21日，政府軍和遜尼派民兵聯手繼續攻擊拉馬迪的重點街區，目標從ISIL手中收復此城<ref>{{cite news|title=Fighting in Iraqi city of Ramadi intensifies|url=http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2014/01/21/346987/fighting-in-iraqi-city-intensifies/|publisher=Press TV|date=21 January 2014|accessdate=2014-02-01|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924134629/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2014/01/21/346987/fighting-in-iraqi-city-intensifies/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隔天，伊拉克國防部表示至少50名武裝份子遭到政府軍空襲陣亡<ref>{{cite news|title=Iraq says air strikes 'kill 50 militants' in Anbar|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-22/244941-iraq-air-strikes-kill-50-militants-in-anbar-ministry.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|publisher=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-22|accessdate=2014-02-01|archive-date=2021-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210211071013/http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-22/244941-iraq-air-strikes-kill-50-militants-in-anbar-ministry.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月26日，根據目擊者表示，ISIL的武裝份子在費盧傑附近俘虜了五名政府軍。ISIL同時於戰鬥後奪取了六臺[[悍馬_(軍用汽車)|悍馬車]]並對其中幾臺縱火燃燒<ref>{{cite news|title=Militants "capture soldiers" as Iraq unrest kills 12|url=https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/mena/532436-militants-capture-soldiers-as-iraq-unrest-kills-12|publisher=NOW|date=2014-01-26|accessdate=2014-02-01|archive-date=2017-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012094713/https://now.mmedia.me/lb/en/mena/532436-militants-capture-soldiers-as-iraq-unrest-kills-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另外也有報導指出費盧傑至少有七人死於政府軍的空襲及砲擊<ref>{{cite news|title=Iraqi planes, artillery strike rebel-held Fallujah|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/01/26/us-iraq-violence-falluja-idUSBREA0P0PX20140126|publisher=Reuters|date=27 January 2014|accessdate=2014-02-01|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924192858/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/01/26/us-iraq-violence-falluja-idUSBREA0P0PX20140126|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

1月30日，伊拉克國防部發言人穆罕默德·阿斯卡里（Mohammad al-Askari）表示政府軍和民兵收復了拉馬迪北方的艾布法拉（Albu Farraj）與西方的納瑟夫（Al-Nasaf）。發言人還表示這些地方對於ISIL的武裝份子是「重要基地」<ref>{{cite news|title=Iraqi forces regain some control of Anbar province|url=http://www.dailystar.com.lb/News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-30/245749-iraqi-forces-regain-some-control-of-anbar-province.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|publisher=The Daily Star|date=2014-01-30|accessdate=2014-02-01|archive-date=2019-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191130144504/http://www.dailystar.com.lb//News/Middle-East/2014/Jan-30/245749-iraqi-forces-regain-some-control-of-anbar-province.ashx#axzz2oNa3sbT8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1月31日，根據伊拉克國防部表示，陸軍第39旅在伊拉克空軍及安巴爾省當地民兵的協助下，擊斃了40名並俘虜四名ISIL武裝份子，同時摧毀該組織在費盧傑的武器<ref>{{cite news|title=Iraqi army kills 40 ISIS fighters in Fallujah|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2014/01/31/Iraqi-army-kills-40-ISIS-fighters-in-Fallujah.html|publisher=[[阿拉伯衛星電視台|阿拉伯衛星電視台]]|date=2014-01-31|accessdate=2014-02-01|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022150750/https://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2014/01/31/Iraqi-army-kills-40-ISIS-fighters-in-Fallujah.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

6月15日，ISIL攻佔{{link-en|薩克拉維亞|Saqlawiyah}}。<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/06/16/uk-iraq-security-idUKKBN0EO0LF20140616?irpc=932 |title=U.S. considers air strikes on Iraq, holds talks with Iran |publisher=Reuters |date=2014-06-16 |accessdate=2014-06-23 |archive-date=2015-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150406090637/http://www.reuters.com/article/2014/06/16/uk-iraq-security-idUKKBN0EO0LF20140616?irpc=932 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

