[[美國|美國]]證實協助伊拉克對抗武裝份子，並加速提供武器設備，其中包括[[AGM-114地獄火飛彈|AGM-114地獄火飛彈]]、[[掃描鷹無人機|掃描鷹無人機]]和[[烏鴉無人機|渡鴉式無人機]]等<ref name=bbc-us-supply>{{cite web|title=Iraq violence: US speeds up supply of military equipment|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-25633629|publisher=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|accessdate=2014-01-07|date=2014-01-07|archive-date=2021-01-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123014708/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-25633629|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，[[伊朗|伊朗]]也提供了支援。伊拉克記者阿里·納席米（Ali Nashmi）也建議例如[[沙烏地阿拉伯|沙烏地阿拉伯]]及[[卡達|卡達]]等[[波斯灣|波斯灣]]國家也能向伊拉克提供協助，以對抗ISIL<ref name="qatar">{{Cite news|url=http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2014/01/17/346175/alqaeda-seeks-iraqi-tribes-help/|title=Al-Qaeda seeks some Iraqi tribes help: Pundit|publisher=Press TV|date=2014-01-17|accessdate=2014-02-01|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924134624/http://www.presstv.ir/detail/2014/01/17/346175/alqaeda-seeks-iraqi-tribes-help/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

